<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Koenigsegg Jesko Guide</title>
  <style>
    /* General Styles */
    body {
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff7e5f, #feb47b); /* Sunset gradient */
      color: #2c3e50; /* Dark text for contrast */
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .container {
      max-width: 1000px;
      margin: 20px auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    h1, h2 {
      color: #e74c3c; /* Sunset red */
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 3rem;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 2px;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 2rem;
      margin-top: 30px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      padding-bottom: 10px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #e74c3c; /* Sunset red */
      display: inline-block;
    }

    p, ul {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #2c3e50;
    }

    ul {
      list-style-type: none;
      padding-left: 0;
    }

    li {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      padding-left: 20px;
      position: relative;
    }

    li::before {
      content: "â€¢";
      color: #e74c3c; /* Sunset red */
      position: absolute;
      left: 0;
    }

    /* Card Styles */
    .card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    /* Images Section */
    .images {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }

    .images img {
      max-width: 60%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
      transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    }

    .images img:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    /* Video Section */
    .video-container {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95); /* Semi-transparent white background */
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
    }

    .video-container iframe {
      max-width: 100%;
      height: 400px;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 5px solid #e74c3c; /* Sunset red */
    }

    /* Responsive Design */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .images img {
        max-width: 100%;
      }

      .video-container iframe {
        height: 250px;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 2.5rem;
      }

      h2 {
        font-size: 1.8rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Koenigsegg Jesko Guide</h1>

    <!-- Overview Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>The Koenigsegg Jesko is a hypercar designed to push the boundaries of speed, performance, and engineering. Named after Christian von Koenigsegg's father, the Jesko is powered by a twin-turbocharged V8 engine and features cutting-edge aerodynamics and lightweight construction. It's a car built for those who demand the absolute best in performance and innovation.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Key Features Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Key Features</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Engine:</strong> 5.0-liter twin-turbocharged V8 producing 1,280 horsepower on standard fuel and 1,600 horsepower on E85.</li>
        <li><strong>Top Speed:</strong> Over 300 mph (483 km/h) in the Jesko Absolut version.</li>
        <li><strong>Acceleration:</strong> 0-60 mph in just 2.5 seconds.</li>
        <li><strong>Weight:</strong> 2,998 lbs (1,360 kg) with extensive use of carbon fiber and lightweight materials.</li>
        <li><strong>Exclusivity:</strong> Limited production run, making it one of the rarest hypercars in the world.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Performance Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Performance</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Power Output:</strong> Up to 1,600 horsepower and 1,106 lb-ft of torque on E85 fuel.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> 9-speed Light Speed Transmission (LST) with ultra-fast gear changes.</li>
        <li><strong>Braking:</strong> Carbon-ceramic brakes for exceptional stopping power.</li>
        <li><strong>Handling:</strong> Advanced aerodynamics and active suspension for maximum grip and stability.</li>
        <li><strong>Track Capability:</strong> Designed to dominate both the road and the track.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Technology Section -->
    <div class="card">
      <h2>Technology</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Aerodynamics:</strong> Active rear wing and front splitter for optimal downforce and stability.</li>
        <li><strong>Transmission:</strong> Revolutionary 9-speed LST with seamless gear changes.</li>
        <li><strong>Lightweight Construction:</strong> Extensive use of carbon fiber and titanium for reduced weight.</li>
        <li><strong>Driver-Centric Design:</strong> Focused on providing an immersive and engaging driving experience.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <!-- Single Image Section -->
    <div class="images">
      <img src="https://f1rst-motors.s3.me-central-1.amazonaws.com/cars/1709547495878-6%20%282%29.webp" alt="Koenigsegg Jesko Image">
    </div>

    <!-- Video Section -->
    <div class="video-container">
      <h2>Learn More About the Koenigsegg Jesko</h2>
      <iframe
        width="560"
        height="400"
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/6xY_LQzTyus" <!-- Replace with a relevant Koenigsegg Jesko video -->
        title="YouTube video player"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>